{"tid":1864481,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(記者入)儲備應急物資 買料自製口罩","createTime":"2020-02-05T15:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T11:35:53.000Z","uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9702ba98c0304895b0f3df90424cc2e65153562c","tid":1864481,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:30:57.000Z","msg":"今次武肺的教訓係每個人要儲備應急物資，今次捱得過，除左要集資起口罩廠，仲要定期儲備應急密資，準備美金買料，天助自助者，不但助己，仲可以助人，黃色應急圈互相送/賣應急物資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1vypMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1vypMU.png&h=5a0d2c0d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n---<br />\n之前睇到有人講用濾網可製口罩，出去揾到3M有出隻靜電空氣濾網，可過濾PM2.5、花粉、細菌、煙霧等，而飛沫係5微米都應該濾到，咁即係同口罩冇分別，我見到係實惠有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYun2yK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYun2yK.png&h=9ae33c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未證實有冇效，冇口罩可試下，但不論有冇效藍屍都唔好學<br />\n<br />\n覺得有用請睇晒下面文宣再轉貼出去<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 榮光自由<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Jy0PdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Jy0PdR.png&h=3a365ddd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziaypNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziaypNc.png&h=11f8b3ea&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n---<br />\n建議光復增設市政警察，環境保護署內設市政警察總隊保護香港資源，總隊隊長向環保署市政副署長負責，食環署環境衞生部分及漁護署漁農部分亦併入環保署<br />\n<br />\n總隊以水警為基礎擴編，負責動物保護、環境保護、水警、漁業農地保護、重建遷移執法、地政非法佔用執法、緊急醫療救護、衞生署及醫管局保安、流行病人入院令執行等，參考入境及救護，體能要求比警察低，比有志者考入政府為民服務<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgxpwS5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgxpwS5.png&h=2e878400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9005c48791c0d9e0a52330c6446ec93d30de9f72","tid":1864481,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9MxFUY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9MxFUY.png&h=b1473d69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f96a0101c6c788974ddcac8f75ccf941d87fd344","tid":1864481,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcRqkyY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcRqkyY.png&h=f2e39d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c1f3c2d82c2d6f68521e4727981168ba252774e","tid":1864481,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"維持新發展反送中企業為主的黃色經濟圈<br />\n建立反送中緊急儲備 保護同路人<br />\n繼續罷藍紅店 攬炒經濟減對家人力及資源"}]}